  "body": "Greetings!\r\n\r\nI synced a fresh new erigon ( `git_branch=HEAD git_tag=v2.43.0 git_commit=1106475e345d936aa1220ace3e95d746ec361fa4` ) with the following parameters:\r\n`--datadir=/mnt/m2/eth --chain=mainnet --port=30304 --http.addr=10.0.0.4 --http.api=eth,erigon,web3,trace,net,debug,admin --http.port=4004 --http.vhosts=* --torrent.download.rate 125mb --rpc.batch.limit=1024`\r\n\r\nSync is finished and the chaindata folder looks like this:\r\n```\r\ndu mdbx.dat\r\n2010604501\tmdbx.dat\r\n```\r\nI have two another erigon node with same erigon version and same db related parameters just with internal cl, these chaindata folder looks like:\r\n```\r\ndu mdbx.dat\r\n990925233\tmdbx.dat\r\n```\r\nI expected less data when i use external CL.\r\n\r\nBr:\r\niFA\r\n",
